WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 9]

01:59.400 --> 02:00.340
When you see these flowers

02:00.880 --> 02:02.300
after you go back,

02:02.680 --> 02:05.220
maybe you'll think of me.

02:45.240 --> 02:46.460
Give Ji Ling back to me.

02:47.400 --> 02:48.140
Give him back!

03:39.360 --> 03:40.180
Submit.

04:05.400 --> 04:06.180
I won't kill you.

04:08.080 --> 04:09.420
But I want to kill you.

04:19.480 --> 04:20.700
You killed Ji Ling.

04:26.560 --> 04:27.900
I'm going to avenge him.

04:29.120 --> 04:30.300
You used the wrong word.

04:31.360 --> 04:33.260
To kill is to take the life of a living being.

04:34.160 --> 04:35.900
Ji Ling was only ever a puppet.

04:36.640 --> 04:37.500
I was the one

04:39.080 --> 04:40.660
who gave him life.

04:41.680 --> 04:44.020
I merely took back what was mine.

04:45.880 --> 04:46.460
Just as I thought.

04:47.960 --> 04:49.700
You've already been corrupted by evil

04:50.520 --> 04:51.580
and strayed from the divine path.

04:53.160 --> 04:54.660
You don't deserve the title of Dragon Deity.

04:57.120 --> 04:58.220
You also deceived Wangyan

04:58.720 --> 05:00.180
and used her to achieve your goals.

05:01.360 --> 05:02.300
Don't try to deny it.

05:03.480 --> 05:04.180
That repulsive scent

05:04.440 --> 05:05.660
on you is something

05:07.680 --> 05:08.700
I'll never forget.

05:12.680 --> 05:13.400
Wangyan,

05:14.360 --> 05:15.770
why do you carry

05:16.120 --> 05:17.710
a strange scent today?

05:19.080 --> 05:20.660
You met her in secret.

05:21.360 --> 05:22.190
Otherwise,

05:22.480 --> 05:24.830
how could she have caught that scent?

05:25.360 --> 05:26.020
So,

05:27.960 --> 05:29.870
you took Wu Wangyan's token

05:31.440 --> 05:32.420
to come settle the score with me?

05:33.560 --> 05:34.620
Who's to say

05:37.080 --> 05:38.460
she didn't give it to me?

05:40.720 --> 05:41.900
She would never give it to you.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.820
What exactly do you want her to do?

05:51.760 --> 05:53.100
You two are close.

05:54.680 --> 05:56.100
Why don't you ask her yourself?

06:02.720 --> 06:03.500
You don't dare.

06:05.040 --> 06:06.180
Because you're afraid.

06:07.120 --> 06:09.420
Afraid you'll hear an answer you don't want.

06:10.360 --> 06:12.460
Afraid she's already betrayed the Formless Moon Sect.

06:13.200 --> 06:14.110
And afraid the sisterly bond

06:14.110 --> 06:15.580
between you two will be severed forever.

06:15.580 --> 06:16.380
Shut up.

06:18.760 --> 06:19.730
No one has ever dared

06:19.800 --> 06:21.860
to be so insolent before me.

06:26.280 --> 06:27.980
Aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

06:29.720 --> 06:30.580
Do you think

06:32.040 --> 06:33.700
you're the only immortal one?

06:34.880 --> 06:35.900
As a Formless Moon member,

06:36.640 --> 06:37.580
even if I die,

06:38.200 --> 06:39.340
once my skin, hair,

06:39.880 --> 06:40.940
blood, and bones

06:41.560 --> 06:42.380
are dissolved

06:42.400 --> 06:43.700
in the Primordial Sacred Spring,

06:45.920 --> 06:46.940
I can be reborn.

06:48.960 --> 06:51.340
Then what if your skin, hair,

06:51.880 --> 06:52.980
blood, and bones

06:54.000 --> 06:55.780
are imprisoned here forever?

07:19.320 --> 07:19.700
Leave.

07:28.640 --> 07:30.140
Tell me your scheme.

08:05.000 --> 08:06.420
Stay by my side and obey me.

08:10.000 --> 08:11.140
Look how weak you are.

08:12.560 --> 08:13.500
Stop fighting.

08:15.280 --> 08:16.420
Stay in the Shilin Sect.

08:17.920 --> 08:19.180
Don't go back and report this.

08:20.840 --> 08:22.620
Don't let my plan fail.

09:30.570 --> 09:32.140
Didn't your sister go look for food?

09:33.200 --> 09:34.220
Why isn't she back yet?

09:45.030 --> 09:46.770
Weren't you supposed to go with me to find the Dragon Deity's Power?

09:48.920 --> 09:50.380
What act are you putting on now?

09:53.280 --> 09:53.940
Relax.

09:55.760 --> 09:56.660
Once I find Wuyi,

09:57.400 --> 09:58.530
I'll come right back

09:59.200 --> 10:00.180
and tell you

10:00.600 --> 10:02.690
where the next strand of the Dragon Deity's Power is.

10:03.440 --> 10:04.780
What if you don't come back?

10:10.960 --> 10:12.060
This is a Moon Summoning Pearl.

10:13.640 --> 10:14.600
Hold it

10:14.880 --> 10:15.780
and channel your sacred power into it,

10:18.280 --> 10:19.330
and no matter how far away I am,

10:20.880 --> 10:23.220
you'll summon me straight back to your side.

10:34.440 --> 10:35.380
I'll believe you one more time.

10:46.240 --> 10:47.580
Could you go wash up?

10:48.760 --> 10:49.620
You stink.

10:51.800 --> 10:52.620
Didn't I just bathe?

11:06.080 --> 11:07.300
I really can't keep carrying you around

11:07.320 --> 11:08.140
anymore.

11:09.600 --> 11:10.980
Your stink is driving all the women away.

11:16.400 --> 11:16.980
Wu Shiguang,

11:18.640 --> 11:19.260
you're done for.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.140
You're in for some real suffering.

11:23.320 --> 11:24.460
The sourness of love

11:24.740 --> 11:25.860
and the bitterness of longing...

11:27.920 --> 11:29.440
Do you know how people are named?

11:30.560 --> 11:31.780
They're usually named to make up

11:32.440 --> 11:33.020
for what they lack.

11:35.920 --> 11:36.420
What do you mean?

11:38.320 --> 11:38.980
Your name is Chi

11:40.120 --> 11:40.660
because you lack "chi."
[*because you're shameless]

12:21.400 --> 12:22.020
Show yourself.

12:25.180 --> 12:29.060
[Si Feng, Greedy Wolf Demon Hunter of the Northern Dipper]

12:33.280 --> 12:34.580
It's been over a century,

12:35.000 --> 12:36.100
and you old demon

12:36.440 --> 12:38.440
still love playing these spooky tricks.

12:39.600 --> 12:42.230
I'm a double-flower hunter of the Shilin Sect.

12:42.310 --> 12:43.020
I'm a human.

12:43.520 --> 12:43.980
You

12:44.440 --> 12:45.380
are the demon.

12:46.920 --> 12:48.200
I've never seen a human

12:48.240 --> 12:49.920
turn half their body

12:49.920 --> 12:51.580
into a puppet.

12:52.530 --> 12:53.460
And

12:53.640 --> 12:54.550
at your age,

12:54.840 --> 12:56.210
you still look this young.

12:56.440 --> 12:57.510
Your beauty-preserving arts

12:57.760 --> 12:59.440
are even better than a demon's skin-changing tricks.

13:01.040 --> 13:02.500
Just what you'd expect from a fox demon.

13:03.400 --> 13:05.900
Even your insults sound flattering.

13:06.240 --> 13:06.700
Tell me.

13:07.120 --> 13:09.580
Why did you burn a summoning talisman to call me out here

13:09.680 --> 13:10.540
in the middle of the night?

13:11.160 --> 13:12.060
To catch up?

13:13.520 --> 13:14.750
My sister took

13:14.750 --> 13:16.000
my Shilin Sect token.

13:16.200 --> 13:17.690
She must've been growing suspicious.

13:19.240 --> 13:20.320
I'm afraid she'll find out

13:21.520 --> 13:23.540
I've been working with the Dragon Deity all along.

13:25.720 --> 13:27.600
Master Chi Wen is stern

13:27.960 --> 13:29.020
and ruthless in all he does.

13:30.360 --> 13:31.460
Your sister is in serious trouble.

13:48.600 --> 13:49.660
Word Magic

13:50.400 --> 13:51.300
only works on those

13:51.320 --> 13:52.620
whose power is weaker than yours.

13:54.200 --> 13:55.820
Otherwise, the blowback can leave you gravely injured.

13:58.080 --> 13:59.340
And once the target

13:59.600 --> 14:00.620
is on guard,

14:01.800 --> 14:03.500
Word Magic hardly works.

14:04.640 --> 14:06.580
Xiaowei's Word Magic was unrivaled.

14:07.320 --> 14:08.700
I carry Xiaowei's power.

14:10.640 --> 14:12.020
How dare you try

14:13.600 --> 14:14.620
to control me?

14:20.480 --> 14:21.060
Ji Ling...

14:33.080 --> 14:34.380
There are many restrictions within the Shilin Sect.

14:35.160 --> 14:36.580
If you don't want your soul annihilated,

14:37.600 --> 14:38.340
stay here.

15:19.520 --> 15:20.140
Here.

15:27.800 --> 15:29.230
These flowers only bloom

15:29.230 --> 15:30.180
in the Shilin Sect.

15:30.560 --> 15:31.140
They're special.

16:54.480 --> 16:55.460
Then let me take you somewhere.

16:55.840 --> 16:56.740
I'm sure it'll cheer you up.

17:08.800 --> 17:09.700
I grew up

17:10.200 --> 17:11.780
by Yumian Lake.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.540
There are lots of delicious raspberries here.

17:16.200 --> 17:17.100
I'll pick some for you in a bit.

17:28.920 --> 17:30.260
Are you sleepy?

17:31.400 --> 17:32.380
Or are you tired

17:32.840 --> 17:34.380
of me talking about all this?

17:35.120 --> 17:35.780
No.

17:38.800 --> 17:39.820
It's just that I hate blood.

17:40.520 --> 17:42.340
I don't want to see blood on my hands.

17:46.720 --> 17:48.660
This world is such a mess.

17:49.120 --> 17:50.060
There are so many things

17:50.400 --> 17:51.260
I don't want to see either.

17:52.080 --> 17:54.530
Death, separation,

17:55.480 --> 17:56.620
injured animals,

17:56.880 --> 17:58.540
forests burned down by mountain fires,

17:59.040 --> 17:59.860
and so many other things...

18:00.200 --> 18:01.220
I couldn't bear to look at them.

18:04.480 --> 18:05.100
But then,

18:05.800 --> 18:07.700
I learned a very useful spell.

18:09.240 --> 18:09.940
What spell?

18:11.560 --> 18:12.460
Make a circle with your hand

18:13.720 --> 18:15.380
and only look at what you like.

18:17.500 --> 18:20.020
♪Who calls my name so clear♪

18:20.340 --> 18:22.660
♪Chasing shadows of the years?♪

18:22.660 --> 18:25.900
♪Sighs of heart, can we dare♪

18:26.260 --> 18:28.020
♪To give her tomorrow fair?♪

18:28.340 --> 18:31.460
♪Tears and joy pile high and wide♪

18:31.580 --> 18:33.900
♪Moonlight bathes her face tonight♪

18:33.980 --> 18:39.860
♪Don't let dew fade before the light♪

18:42.940 --> 18:44.900
♪In deep snow♪

18:45.380 --> 18:47.740
♪We in red robes, with white hair♪

18:48.180 --> 18:52.460
♪Gaze at the shimmering distant hills, lost in their glow♪

18:53.700 --> 18:54.700
♪Moonlit one♪

18:55.100 --> 18:58.860
♪You always make my heart race beyond all restraint♪

18:59.300 --> 19:03.860
♪Let snowflakes be my kisses♪

19:05.420 --> 19:10.340
♪The lovestruck fear not pity, but love laid bare♪

19:10.620 --> 19:15.260
♪Let love and hate be carved into my bones♪

19:16.180 --> 19:21.460
♪The whole city bears the scars of years gone by♪

19:21.740 --> 19:26.460
♪And every ring of time bears our traces♪

19:27.980 --> 19:29.780
♪The wind carries her far away...♪

19:30.240 --> 19:31.340
I picked these out for you.

19:31.680 --> 19:32.300
They're sweet.

19:33.540 --> 19:38.060
♪Back to his side to see him once more...♪

19:40.760 --> 19:41.260
Here.

19:43.640 --> 19:44.580
A bouquet

19:45.040 --> 19:45.740
of fresh wildflowers

19:46.280 --> 19:47.460
fully in bloom.

19:48.480 --> 19:49.340
Cheer up.

19:50.060 --> 19:52.380
♪We count down to tomorrow♪

19:52.740 --> 19:55.100
♪Life and death beyond the distant snowy mountains♪

19:55.180 --> 19:58.460
♪Silent and wordless, on opposite shores♪

19:58.620 --> 20:00.700
♪We bow to eternity...♪

20:03.560 --> 20:04.300
Forget me.

20:06.380 --> 20:12.260
♪The story opens with regret and ends with parting♪

20:12.420 --> 20:14.940
♪Let's go back in time♪

20:15.300 --> 20:17.580
♪Snow piled high by the window♪

20:17.660 --> 20:20.940
♪Under sparks of fireworks, we♪

20:21.060 --> 20:23.260
♪Smiled through tears so sweet♪

20:23.380 --> 20:26.460
♪You said you'd find a little corner♪

20:26.500 --> 20:28.780
♪And give me ten thousand wildflowers♪

20:28.820 --> 20:34.700
♪Softly telling me you'd stay with me forever♪

20:41.600 --> 20:42.380
Why are you crying?

20:52.330 --> 20:53.270
I'm not.

20:55.520 --> 20:56.900
Then why are your eyes red?

21:00.240 --> 21:01.800
A pungent smell

21:02.090 --> 21:03.220
irritated them.

21:04.880 --> 21:06.380
You've been making things up.

21:07.040 --> 21:09.020
Why do you keep saying I carry

21:09.760 --> 21:10.900
a strange scent?

21:12.760 --> 21:13.500
Making things up?

21:16.120 --> 21:17.220
Can't you smell it yourself?

21:19.040 --> 21:20.460
I follow a vegetarian diet,

21:21.000 --> 21:22.220
and I bathe and change clothes every day.

21:22.960 --> 21:23.740
Other than you,

21:24.200 --> 21:25.860
no one has ever said

21:25.920 --> 21:27.260
there's anything strange about my scent.

21:28.960 --> 21:30.660
Maybe they've been around you so long

21:31.440 --> 21:32.340
their sense of smell has gone wrong.

21:33.200 --> 21:34.380
Don't be insolent

21:35.320 --> 21:36.340
before me.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.140
How long are you going to keep me here?

21:49.440 --> 21:50.100
This won't work.

21:51.320 --> 21:52.700
On the next night of the full moon,

21:53.320 --> 21:54.220
the Oracle Stone's power

21:54.480 --> 21:55.980
will summon me back to the Formless Moon.

21:56.720 --> 21:58.380
Do you really think you can trap me

21:59.960 --> 22:00.740
in this pathetic sect?

22:05.000 --> 22:05.940
You can try.

22:11.120 --> 22:11.620
Ji Ling.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.700
Will I ever see him again?

22:20.280 --> 22:21.140
Didn't you say

22:25.920 --> 22:26.780
I was him?

22:30.960 --> 22:32.240
I want to see the Ji Ling

22:32.240 --> 22:33.480
who always had a smile on his face,

22:35.480 --> 22:37.060
who was warm and kind.

22:39.480 --> 22:40.580
Am I never

22:44.040 --> 22:45.380
going to see him again?

22:49.060 --> 22:53.300
♪Who turned away, leaving only a back to hold?♪

22:54.300 --> 22:57.020
♪Face unseen, voice unheard♪

22:57.580 --> 23:02.700
♪Youth in twilight, a soul aging too soon♪

23:03.140 --> 23:05.500
♪Burning over and over♪

23:05.860 --> 23:09.820
♪The flower in the mirror fades as I sketch it♪

23:10.300 --> 23:14.260
♪I remember the old days as I forget them♪

23:14.580 --> 23:18.020
♪You left behind your final words♪

23:18.420 --> 23:25.060
♪And every word became a scar♪

23:26.920 --> 23:28.040
People worship you

23:28.920 --> 23:29.640
and place their faith in you,

23:30.760 --> 23:32.890
never knowing you've long lost your mercy

23:33.040 --> 23:34.180
and divinity.

23:35.000 --> 23:36.940
And you still had the nerve to put up your own statue here

23:37.880 --> 23:39.810
to receive offerings,

23:40.000 --> 23:41.250
bows, and worship from the hunters?

23:44.360 --> 23:45.800
Shameless.

24:44.400 --> 24:45.240
Lu Wuyi

24:45.240 --> 24:46.300
really is fearless.

24:47.440 --> 24:48.350
A demon

24:48.680 --> 24:49.660
barging into the Shilin Sect?

24:50.320 --> 24:51.500
How's that different from a chicken

24:51.720 --> 24:53.300
charging into a weasel's den and crowing

24:53.320 --> 24:54.140
at the top of its lungs?

24:54.480 --> 24:55.530
Still,

24:55.560 --> 24:56.740
someone as mighty as the Dragon Deity

24:57.040 --> 24:58.300
wouldn't lock up a young girl

24:58.480 --> 24:59.300
and torture her,

25:00.360 --> 25:01.500
would he?

25:03.800 --> 25:04.660
Hasn't he done plenty

25:05.600 --> 25:06.220
of evil already?

25:06.440 --> 25:09.660
But surely he'd at least feed her, right?

25:12.520 --> 25:13.460
The food at the Shilin Sect

25:14.960 --> 25:16.220
doesn't even have a drop of oil in it.

25:17.640 --> 25:18.380
Even dogs wouldn't eat it.

26:00.800 --> 26:02.790
I fell asleep in the Dragon Deity Palace last night.

26:03.160 --> 26:04.380
Which one of you brought me back?

26:05.160 --> 26:06.110
The Dragon Deity Palace

26:06.160 --> 26:07.600
is a solemn, sacred place.

26:07.800 --> 26:08.590
You're not allowed to sleep there.

26:10.600 --> 26:12.460
I... I brought you back.

26:13.240 --> 26:13.980
I used magic

26:14.600 --> 26:15.900
to bring you back.

26:17.680 --> 26:18.420
You?

26:23.720 --> 26:24.100
Me.

26:26.480 --> 26:27.700
What's your name?

26:29.320 --> 26:30.220
My name is Ye Changsheng.

26:30.800 --> 26:32.180
I'm Master Chi Wen's attendant.

26:32.720 --> 26:33.620
My grandfather was an attendant too.

26:34.000 --> 26:34.860
My family has served

26:35.080 --> 26:36.980
Master Chi Wen for three generations.

26:39.320 --> 26:40.380
Ye Changsheng?
[*Changsheng: longevity]

26:41.720 --> 26:43.460
I'm a fox demon that eats people.

26:46.280 --> 26:48.020
If you stick around, you can kiss longevity goodbye.

26:48.280 --> 26:48.620
I...

26:50.040 --> 26:51.420
Breakfast is ready, Miss Lu.

26:52.400 --> 26:54.120
I bought all this from a restaurant outside,

26:54.400 --> 26:55.820
since our food may be too light for your liking.

26:56.440 --> 26:56.820
Take a look.

26:59.000 --> 27:00.220
Did Chi Wen tell you to buy this?

27:04.080 --> 27:05.620
I... I bought it myself.

27:06.000 --> 27:06.540
You?

27:08.000 --> 27:08.680
What,

27:09.280 --> 27:10.070
do you like me?

27:10.120 --> 27:10.680
No...

27:10.880 --> 27:12.070
Miss, please don't say things like that.

27:12.160 --> 27:12.420
I...

27:13.880 --> 27:14.650
Does it suit your taste?

27:14.880 --> 27:15.550
If there's nothing else,

27:15.600 --> 27:16.940
I'll be going now.

27:26.920 --> 27:27.260
Why

27:28.040 --> 27:28.700
aren't you eating?

27:30.080 --> 27:31.220
I'm worried you poisoned it.

27:43.440 --> 27:45.100
Then I really don't get it.

27:45.840 --> 27:47.180
You lock me up here

27:47.180 --> 27:48.150
as a prisoner.

27:49.150 --> 27:50.850
Why did you prepare such a feast

27:51.000 --> 27:51.740
for me?

27:52.400 --> 27:54.020
Master Chi Wen only said

27:54.360 --> 27:55.580
you'd be staying at the Shilin Sect

27:55.600 --> 27:56.300
for a while.

27:56.630 --> 27:57.820
He never said you were a prisoner.

27:59.280 --> 28:00.610
I can't even move around at will.

28:01.070 --> 28:02.160
If I'm not a prisoner, what am I?

28:02.830 --> 28:04.540
The only thing missing is a pair of shackles.

28:05.320 --> 28:06.580
Where is Chi Wen?

28:08.240 --> 28:09.690
I can't finish

28:09.840 --> 28:10.980
all this good food by myself.

28:11.600 --> 28:12.660
Tell him to come eat with me.

28:13.200 --> 28:14.020
Master Chi Wen

28:14.200 --> 28:15.300
never dines with others.

28:15.880 --> 28:17.060
Normally, Commander Li

28:17.080 --> 28:18.500
attends to Master Chi Wen during meals,

28:18.920 --> 28:20.020
because there are simply

28:20.040 --> 28:21.540
too many demons who want to harm him.

28:21.760 --> 28:22.580
To be safe,

28:22.760 --> 28:24.420
he only eats food delivered by Commander Li.

28:24.480 --> 28:25.210
No exceptions.

28:25.680 --> 28:26.850
But

28:28.120 --> 28:30.270
only a dragon can kill a dragon.

28:31.040 --> 28:32.330
Why would he worry

28:32.330 --> 28:33.380
about others poisoning him?

28:33.520 --> 28:35.380
Even if the poison wouldn't kill him,

28:35.880 --> 28:36.860
it would still feel awful.

28:58.600 --> 28:59.780
Is it that bad?

29:02.960 --> 29:03.980
It's so good.

29:04.560 --> 29:05.980
Back at the Formless Moon,

29:06.000 --> 29:07.490
we could only eat fruits and vegetables.

29:07.490 --> 29:09.230
But here, you're feeding me so well.

29:09.440 --> 29:10.780
Now that I've tasted luxury,

29:11.400 --> 29:12.540
how am I supposed

29:12.880 --> 29:14.290
to go back to eating simple meals?

29:14.880 --> 29:15.940
I... I'll take my leave now.

29:23.280 --> 29:24.060
It's already morning.

29:25.240 --> 29:26.490
I've been trying to reassure you all night.

29:26.800 --> 29:27.980
Why are you still so worried?

29:29.200 --> 29:30.940
Wuyi has never suffered or been wronged

29:31.240 --> 29:32.020
a day in her life.

29:33.120 --> 29:33.900
She's probably being

29:34.880 --> 29:36.100
tortured at the Shilin Sect right now.

29:42.160 --> 29:43.940
Yunjin brocade quilts

29:44.400 --> 29:45.300
and a soft pillow made of golden silk.

29:45.960 --> 29:46.820
Are these

29:47.120 --> 29:48.100
to your liking, Miss Lu?

29:49.280 --> 29:51.060
This is nowhere near as nice as what we have

29:51.160 --> 29:52.220
at the Formless Moon.

29:52.950 --> 29:55.570
This is already the best the Shilin Sect

29:55.570 --> 29:56.540
can offer.

29:58.720 --> 29:59.500
The best?

30:01.280 --> 30:02.860
What good are pillows and quilts alone?

30:03.640 --> 30:05.140
I don't even have a change of clothes.

30:06.040 --> 30:07.870
All I have is this shabby robe.

30:09.080 --> 30:09.860
It's hideous.

30:10.320 --> 30:11.980
This isn't some shabby robe.

30:12.920 --> 30:13.380
It's...

30:14.200 --> 30:14.500
it's...

30:21.720 --> 30:23.220
Do you have any other requests, Miss Lu?

30:23.840 --> 30:24.660
Master Chi Wen said

30:25.120 --> 30:26.020
we were to do whatever you ask.

30:26.440 --> 30:27.820
So what exactly is he playing at?

30:28.800 --> 30:30.540
A stick, and then a carrot?

30:31.040 --> 30:32.020
Save it.

30:32.640 --> 30:34.060
I don't accept charity.

30:34.480 --> 30:35.300
Let me make one thing clear.

30:35.960 --> 30:38.060
Don't think you can wear down my resolve

30:39.440 --> 30:41.220
with fine clothes and good food.

30:41.840 --> 30:43.180
Even if the Dragon Deity doesn't mistreat her,

30:43.480 --> 30:44.860
there are so many hunters in the Shilin Sect

30:45.120 --> 30:46.220
who hate demons to the bone.

30:46.680 --> 30:48.340
They'll definitely bully Wuyi

30:48.600 --> 30:49.460
in secret.

30:50.720 --> 30:51.340
Miss Lu,

30:52.080 --> 30:53.980
are you pleased with this incense?

30:59.160 --> 31:00.220
It smells wonderful.

31:01.440 --> 31:02.620
Life at the Shilin Sect

31:03.600 --> 31:04.820
is way too comfortable.

31:05.400 --> 31:06.160
Fine.

31:06.480 --> 31:07.220
I promise.

31:07.640 --> 31:08.900
I'll go back to the Shilin Sect and check on her for you.

31:09.720 --> 31:10.260
But

31:10.640 --> 31:12.140
the next full moon is almost here.

31:12.840 --> 31:13.940
Your memories will be shared at the Sacred Spring.

31:14.600 --> 31:16.340
How are you going to keep your secrets from the other members?

31:17.920 --> 31:18.580
It doesn't matter.

31:19.320 --> 31:19.980
At worst,

31:20.680 --> 31:21.740
I'll do what Xiaowei did

31:22.160 --> 31:23.100
and cut off a tail to survive.

31:24.000 --> 31:25.580
The Never-Ending Curse will hunt you forever.

31:25.960 --> 31:27.080
You'll have to lose a sense,

31:27.280 --> 31:28.240
live in anonymity,

31:28.360 --> 31:29.460
and become an ordinary woman

31:29.460 --> 31:30.620
who doesn't dare use demon magic.

31:31.400 --> 31:32.100
Do you really want that?

31:33.200 --> 31:34.020
Living like a mortal

31:35.720 --> 31:37.020
is exactly what I've always wanted.

31:38.640 --> 31:39.680
Chi Wen

31:39.680 --> 31:41.080
thinks I'm some demoness

31:41.440 --> 31:42.620
who has done all kinds of evil

31:42.800 --> 31:43.970
and endangered the people,

31:44.880 --> 31:46.740
so he locked me up in the Shilin Sect.

31:47.920 --> 31:49.260
But as a demon,

31:50.280 --> 31:52.340
I'm not used to sleeping on Yunjin brocade and fine silk.

31:54.200 --> 31:54.580
Then...

31:55.720 --> 31:57.980
then what are you used to sleeping on, Miss Lu?

32:00.480 --> 32:01.140
As a demon,

32:02.680 --> 32:03.500
of course I'm used to sleeping

32:03.600 --> 32:05.620
on things far bloodier and more terrifying.

32:06.040 --> 32:07.460
It helps with cultivating demon magic.

32:08.320 --> 32:09.260
For example,

32:11.000 --> 32:11.860
human skin.

32:12.700 --> 32:13.210
What?

32:22.600 --> 32:24.100
You've got some nerve.

32:25.720 --> 32:26.770
I heard

32:27.160 --> 32:28.140
Chi Wen

32:28.160 --> 32:29.340
was injured in a brutal battle

32:30.160 --> 32:31.460
and needed to absorb humans' life force to recover.

32:32.000 --> 32:32.420
Miss Lu,

32:32.880 --> 32:33.460
you mustn't speak nonsense.

32:34.160 --> 32:36.180
Master Chi Wen is the Dragon Deity who protects all living beings.

32:36.480 --> 32:37.820
He holds kindness and compassion

32:38.000 --> 32:39.380
for every creature in the world.

32:40.600 --> 32:41.620
You must not slander him.

32:42.920 --> 32:45.250
I didn't realize you were this loyal to Chi Wen.

32:46.320 --> 32:48.380
When we of the Formless Moon carried out missions,

32:48.800 --> 32:49.710
we disguised ourselves

32:49.710 --> 32:51.340
as Shilin Sect members more than once.

32:51.880 --> 32:53.470
I like how smooth

32:53.920 --> 32:54.980
your skin is.

32:55.760 --> 32:56.940
When I get the chance next time, I'll use it.

32:58.000 --> 32:58.780
Give it to me.

32:59.600 --> 33:01.370
Master Chi Wen, help!

33:08.760 --> 33:09.740
You can trap me here,

33:11.200 --> 33:13.700
but no one in the Shilin Sect is getting any peace either.

33:16.520 --> 33:17.860
Let's torture each other

33:19.080 --> 33:19.900
and see who lasts longer.

33:35.600 --> 33:37.100
It's just been one night,

33:38.080 --> 33:39.420
Shiguang,

33:40.760 --> 33:42.410
and you already can't resist

33:42.510 --> 33:43.790
using my

33:44.740 --> 33:45.870
Moon Summoning Pearl?

33:49.730 --> 33:51.120
Did you miss me that much?

33:54.560 --> 33:55.970
Do all you foxes from the Formless Moon

33:57.030 --> 33:57.980
talk

33:58.880 --> 33:59.940
in this halting,

34:00.520 --> 34:01.830
syrupy way?

34:07.160 --> 34:07.700
Where's Lu Wuyi?

34:10.480 --> 34:11.700
She's grown up and gotten rebellious.

34:13.200 --> 34:14.220
She has ideas of her own.

34:14.880 --> 34:15.420
Let's go.

34:17.280 --> 34:17.700
Go where?

34:19.520 --> 34:20.460
The Ruined Sand.

34:21.320 --> 34:22.740
That's where the next strand

34:24.640 --> 34:26.020
of the Dragon Deity's Power is.

34:27.400 --> 34:28.140
Help him.

34:29.160 --> 34:30.140
Earn his trust.

34:31.600 --> 34:32.180
Then

34:33.960 --> 34:34.940
take the prayer beads.

34:39.280 --> 34:39.700
What is it?

34:41.080 --> 34:42.420
You know that place?

34:59.400 --> 35:00.500
No return.

35:01.800 --> 35:02.980
No finding it again.

35:05.680 --> 35:07.380
No matter how many times I perform the divination,

35:09.480 --> 35:10.460
the result

35:12.840 --> 35:13.780
is always the same.

35:22.320 --> 35:23.640
How much longer are you going to wait

35:24.040 --> 35:25.840
before you fulfill your promise

35:26.080 --> 35:27.870
and make the Star Stone shine again?

35:37.440 --> 35:39.140
You said that once the Star Stone became whole,

35:39.960 --> 35:41.300
it would shine again

35:44.690 --> 35:46.120
and free my people

35:46.440 --> 35:48.530
from the Petrification Curse.

35:49.290 --> 35:51.090
That's why I broke my oath

35:51.480 --> 35:53.430
and took back the power I lent the Dragon Deity.

35:54.580 --> 35:55.810
So why

36:01.480 --> 36:02.620
isn't it working?

36:09.660 --> 36:10.660
Because we still have to wait

36:10.680 --> 36:12.420
for the man with the Twelve Thoughts.

36:38.520 --> 36:39.980
Don't you get bored sitting in meditation all day?

36:41.600 --> 36:42.980
Come pick some fresh flowers with me,

36:43.680 --> 36:44.140
will you?

36:45.560 --> 36:46.020
No.

36:48.320 --> 36:49.340
Then I'll go by myself.

36:49.840 --> 36:50.260
Stop.

36:53.160 --> 36:53.940
You're not going either.

36:55.640 --> 36:57.460
Don't force me to use Word Magic on you again.

37:01.440 --> 37:03.300
My power may be weaker than yours,

37:04.120 --> 37:04.940
but I'm

37:04.960 --> 37:06.700
on guard against you every second now.

37:07.280 --> 37:08.520
It won't be that easy

37:09.590 --> 37:10.500
for you to control me.

37:25.320 --> 37:26.860
That demoness defiled the Dragon Deity's statue.

37:27.280 --> 37:28.260
I've been scrubbing it for three days,

37:28.280 --> 37:29.140
and it still won't come clean.

37:29.680 --> 37:30.340
She's infuriating!

37:34.000 --> 37:35.780
Please, stop drawing on it!

37:46.600 --> 37:48.830
She said she wanted rootless water.

37:49.040 --> 37:50.700
I want rootless water,

37:51.960 --> 37:53.140
dustless fruit,

37:55.320 --> 37:56.500
and scentless incense.

37:56.720 --> 37:57.940
How was I supposed to know what those were?

37:58.200 --> 38:00.020
She was obviously making things difficult on purpose.

38:00.240 --> 38:01.580
She said I peeked while she was changing.

38:02.000 --> 38:02.660
Good grief!

38:02.800 --> 38:04.440
Who changes clothes in the hallway?

38:07.120 --> 38:08.020
What's wrong with you,

38:08.240 --> 38:09.500
peeking at a young girl changing clothes?

38:10.360 --> 38:11.460
How shameless.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.710
I almost gouged out my own eyes!

38:17.000 --> 38:17.460
Commander Li,

38:17.680 --> 38:18.660
please talk to the Dragon Deity

38:19.360 --> 38:20.260
so he lets her go soon.

38:20.480 --> 38:22.570
If she doesn't leave, I will.

38:22.640 --> 38:23.400
She's unbearable,

38:23.680 --> 38:25.740
evil to the core!

38:47.920 --> 38:48.790
What's with that look?

38:51.320 --> 38:52.180
Three words

38:53.040 --> 38:53.820
describe you perfectly

38:53.920 --> 38:54.820
right now.

39:00.560 --> 39:01.220
Which three?

39:03.080 --> 39:04.020
Undignified old man.

39:06.880 --> 39:07.220
I...

39:21.600 --> 39:22.780
This is no sparring match.

39:22.920 --> 39:24.260
This is bullying!

39:25.320 --> 39:27.300
Chi Wen has such a good temper.

39:28.360 --> 39:29.750
I've caused this much commotion,

39:30.080 --> 39:31.570
and he still won't come out to stop me.

39:31.680 --> 39:33.620
If he won't stop you, I will!

40:12.560 --> 40:13.780
This is Shilin Sect territory.

40:14.560 --> 40:16.340
How dare a demoness like you run wild here?

40:17.400 --> 40:18.420
If you don't want me running wild,

40:19.000 --> 40:20.180
tell him to let me go.

40:20.560 --> 40:21.540
He doesn't dare kill me

40:21.920 --> 40:23.020
for fear of angering the Formless Moon,

40:23.480 --> 40:25.140
but he's also afraid I'll expose his true colors,

40:25.920 --> 40:27.220
so he traps me here.

40:28.440 --> 40:29.500
But what's the point?

40:30.600 --> 40:31.700
When the full moon comes,

40:32.120 --> 40:33.140
I'll still be able to leave.

40:33.600 --> 40:34.180
Shut up.

41:02.080 --> 41:03.540
Greetings, Master Chi Wen.

41:06.400 --> 41:07.340
Come with me.

41:09.440 --> 41:10.300
Get moving already.

41:17.160 --> 41:18.100
I was talking to you.

41:19.280 --> 41:19.900
Come with me.

41:22.840 --> 41:24.140
And if I don't want to?

41:24.960 --> 41:25.860
Are you going to

41:26.320 --> 41:27.620
tie me up, Master Chi Wen?

42:38.780 --> 42:39.940
♪It's your light♪

42:40.140 --> 42:42.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

42:42.180 --> 42:45.300
♪That set the night alight♪

42:45.660 --> 42:52.180
♪And lead me through the fight♪

42:53.940 --> 42:55.820
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

42:56.260 --> 43:00.700
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:01.500 --> 43:03.180
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:03.340 --> 43:08.740
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:09.500 --> 43:14.900
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:17.220 --> 43:23.260
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:24.220 --> 43:26.380
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:26.660 --> 43:31.500
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:31.860 --> 43:34.180
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

43:34.380 --> 43:39.460
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

43:39.700 --> 43:41.700
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

43:41.980 --> 43:46.340
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

43:47.340 --> 43:54.300
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:10.860 --> 44:13.820
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:14.900 --> 44:18.300
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:19.100 --> 44:21.620
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:21.860 --> 44:24.940
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:25.340 --> 44:27.660
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:28.180 --> 44:32.580
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:32.820 --> 44:34.980
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

44:35.380 --> 44:40.340
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

44:40.580 --> 44:41.740
♪It's your light♪

44:41.940 --> 44:43.780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:43.980 --> 44:47.100
♪That set the night alight♪

44:47.860 --> 44:57.300
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
